com.mousebird.maply

Class Point3d

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.Point3d

  • public class Point3d
extends java.lang.Object
    The Point3d class is your standard x,y,z container. The only thing of note here is this is a wrapper for the interal Maply 3D point class.
